The Business Model
You'd charge:
Transaction fee: 1.5% + KES 5 per successful charge
Monthly SaaS fee: KES 5,000/month for advanced features (analytics, dunning, proration)
Setup: Free (self-serve)
Bottom Line
Recurring billing = charging customers automatically on a schedule.
The opportunity: African payment gateways don't handle the complexity well. SaaS companies need someone to solve this.
